Dynamic Inventory Management: Uses a linked list to easily add, remove, and display all books in the library's collection.

Core Circulation System: Allows users to borrow and return books, which instantly updates their availability status.

Reversible Actions: Includes an undo feature powered by a stack that can instantly reverse the last borrow or return command.

Quick Search Functionality: Provides a simple way to search and filter the entire inventory by book title or author.
